Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.96,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you call me by the \Nname of the Jealous Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Because you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:28.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who told you that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but they have terrible taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,The Jealous Witch is the epitome of taboo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:36.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and you call me by her name, \Nwhich most dare not even say!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:37.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:38.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's going too far, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:43.35,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nothing to say, I'm leaving. \NI have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:49.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Were you stalling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:05.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You have it all wrong! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:15.78,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Could someone just treat me a little nicer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I even...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,summoned to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.53,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:10.48,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get hurt, cough up \Nwhatever you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No one is this damn persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.42,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can mouth off to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:23.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way! I have somewhere I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.80,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Man, now you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.81,Default - upper,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,You stabbed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.66,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.24,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.86,Default - upper,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! He walked right into my blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.89,Default - upper,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.62,Default - upper,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no sense in wasting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.85,Default - upper,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Take anything on him that's worth selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:46.85,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:50.03,Default - upper,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! The guards will be here any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.69,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But Old Man Rom ate those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.42,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.78,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could... this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.30,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Run! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.73,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, boy? You want this appa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.22,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you seen me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.53,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.62,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are you buying it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm broke beyond compare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.63,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wallet, cell phone, corn potage snack, cup noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:42.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My tracksuit and sneakers are intact, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:51.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god. A wound to the back \Nis a warrior's greatest shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with so much circumstantial \Nevidence, there's no denying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda hard to believe, but this has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A time leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And each time, I return to my initial state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Return by Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I actually get a time-leap ability, \Nand it only activates when I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:21.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The precondition being pitiful is so typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:28.28,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I've gone back in time, Satella hasn't \Nhelped me in this fourth life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.51,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning the debt I owed her for saving me is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:37.13,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should forget everything, sell this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:41.02,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,save some funds, and use my knowledge \Nof the modern world to live in luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is taking shape before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get caught up \Nin other people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:03.59,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess "Let sleeping dogs \Nlie," applies in any world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.88,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But still, there are always softies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.35,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,who help others, even when \Nthey really can't afford to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.16,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She'd just had something precious stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.45,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't have time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.52,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she saved some useless stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.77,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and even healed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.50,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then she let that useless stranger \Nbe pleased with himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.34,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Satella doesn't know me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.43,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felt still stole her insignia. And Elsa will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.82,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I repeat \Nthis, that won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.25,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They say history repeats itself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.57,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.87,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I have knowledge that people \NI used to know will be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.83,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just ignore it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.65,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, broke kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have there been any pickpocketing \Nincidents around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:38.04,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Asking questions, without buying anything? \NYou really do have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.65,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Incidents like that aren't uncommon at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.61,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Though, that last one was unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:48.07,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,They threw some magic around \Nin the street a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.01,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Things that looked like icicles flew \Naround and lodged in the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.49,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,But they disappeared fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I could keep the insignia \Nfrom being stolen, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.27,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just talking to myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:06.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister... For telling me, \Neven though I didn't buy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.21,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:13.98,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,A broke kid, like you, just helped my \Ndaughter after she got lost earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:18.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess fate is a compelling force, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.39,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy an appa next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.52,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Buy one, and you'll be a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.06,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work, broke kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:29.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This means there's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before Elsa comes to the loot house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to buy the insignia from \NFelt, and return it to Satella!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:38.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Satella was just an alias, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:47.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've gotta get her to tell \Nme her real name this time—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.09,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.28,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get hurt, cough up \Nwhatever you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting sick of seeing your faces, \NLarry, Moe, and Curly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After doing this four times, \NI've learned my lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.86,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.49,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My memory from before was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.82,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This world does have some kind of police force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:23.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! P-Please, I need a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.54,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't touch me... Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you. You're not being sincere enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:33.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Police... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.23,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.87,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,I might have freaked out, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.51,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.05,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tiny, little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.14,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to run won't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.10,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.42,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Red hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.63,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,And a knight's sword, with scratches \Nmade by dragon claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.11,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.10,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.33,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,The master swordsman, Reinhard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.24,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Seems I needn't introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.78,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Although, that nickname is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:13.19,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much my modest \Nstrength could aid him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.85,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But if you wish to resort to extreme measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.93,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,as a knight, I would have to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:23.24,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,S-Screw this! It's not worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.06,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we're both safe. Are you unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:38.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A-Allow me to thank you, from the bottom \Nof my heart, for saving my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:42.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I, Natsuki Subaru, \Ndeeply admire your selflessness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.91,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,No need for such formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:50.05,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Once it was three against two, \Nthey lost their advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.23,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been alone, it would have been different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.89,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-His nice-guy index is off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:02.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Reinhard-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.81,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,You may just call me "Reinhard," Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.86,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,He closed our distance like it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks again, Reinhard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:14.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who heard me \Nshouting and came to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:21.09,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,For most, it's too risky to face off \Nagainst people like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.63,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,As far as it goes, you were \Nright to call for the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.94,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off duty today, so I'm not in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.90,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,And I realize that I don't appear \Nparticularly intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:41.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, didn't they \Ncall you a master swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.22,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,My family is fairly unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.57,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, I feel I'll be crushed \Nby their expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.26,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:53.86,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the unusual \Nhair, apparel, and name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.36,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,What nation are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.62,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, Lugunica is a bit \Nmore restive than in peacetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.91,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem, I'd be glad to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come to the loot house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.49,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The loot house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:12.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind... Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trouble you with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the rest on my own, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'd appreciate it if you \Ncould deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.75,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.14,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,To whom? And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know her name, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:34.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen a girl with white \Nrobes and silver hair nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.32,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,White robes and silver hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's also extremely gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.20,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you do see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,tell her not to go near the loot \Nhouse, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:53.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find what she's looking for \Nand bring it to her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.74,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. If I see her, \NI shall relay your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.17,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.33,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Felt's den?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:14.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just go two streets down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I appreciate it, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:20.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it, bro. Live strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:24.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The question is whether Felt will return there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather catch her before she \Ngoes to the loot house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and trade her the cell phone for the insignia—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:31.99,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.39,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look it, but toughness \Nis one thing I... have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.77,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.89,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so scared. \NI won't do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What gave you that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:58.99,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Your scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:04.48,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,When people are scared, I can smell their fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.27,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.20,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You're also angry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.64,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.08,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:25.78,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little curious, but this isn't \Nthe time to start a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a very nice thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too scary, \Nthat beauty will go to waste—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.25,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.85,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Conceal your hostility, \Nand you'll be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.04,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.98,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Something tells me we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone actually lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:07.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Elsa hasn't already been here \Nand trashed it, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't smell blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But it does smell like garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:18.79,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, \Npeeking into someone's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:22.98,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but there's nothing worth stealing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:23.98,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! That's not what I was doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.70,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! This is no time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before it gets dark—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Before it gets dark, you'd better be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you've got it all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.85,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.32,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Just hear me out, Felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you on important business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.67,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.63,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to steal something for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.19,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, this is a greedy business you're running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you pride yourself on sticky fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.59,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a matter of how to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.28,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't this, I'd have no \Nchoice but to sell my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.12,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.30,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Here and now, I want to buy the insignia you stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:45.75,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't associated with my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.31,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a business rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Call her a rival, or call her the \None who killed my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Or even the one who killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.57,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:17:00.47,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm only interested in selling \Nto whoever pays most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.73,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got an offer that might \Nbe profitable, I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Very shrewd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:10.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have something worth more \Nthan twenty holy coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy your insignia with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's what everyone wants these days, a metia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That is the power of a metia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:26.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-of-a-kind item that can capture \Nand stop a moment in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.01,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.70,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,But that's supposed to be me?\N I'm way prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you look this good without makeup, \Nyou're doing fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.24,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is unusual. I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:43.71,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,But twenty holy coins? Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.89,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so stupid as to believe, without question,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.51,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,everything a prospective buyer says.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.38,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,At the far edge of the slums is a loot house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.76,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,The fair thing is to have the codger who \Nlives there, Old Man Rom, appraise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So it still comes to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now... Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:12.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have him take a look, \Nand get right out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:12.94,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.20,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.73,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.62,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.68,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Live strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the slums says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of slogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.74,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me in with those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,They're all talk. They aren't strong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:41.30,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,They're just a bunch of \Nstingy losers at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.88,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.40,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of living out \Nmy life in these back alleys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:19:00.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And you think twenty holy coins will \Nmake your dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:04.43,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it'd be a \Nhuge leap toward my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:08.00,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I were alone, it isn't as \Nif I couldn't get by with effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you were alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.54,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.39,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What are you smirking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.27,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You really piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what're you doing? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just gotta make it work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.34,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Stop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And only I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:35.21,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get all sentimental and babble nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.37,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.34,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't only for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.15,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change the fate that's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.50,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.56,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.82,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a metia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.94,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Even I've never seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's fairly delicate, so handle it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:07.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Think along the lines of, "If you \Nbreak it, you have to die,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,like no do-overs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:12.06,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm definitely impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:19.56,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to sell this, I'd take no less than fifteen... no, twenty holy coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.43,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth at least that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:24.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Negotiations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:30.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if we're done talking, let's go for \Ndrinks to celebrate a completed sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:31.94,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.51,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Life doesn't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Make every second count. Don't waste any—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.36,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.13,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:48.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you even want the insignia, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.98,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,This insignia is worth a lot more than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.35,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.48,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this would sell \Nfor more than a metia—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Felt! That's a dangerous way to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,He appraised it at over twenty holy coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:09.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just sell it for that! Don't ask for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:13.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,El— The woman who asked you for it \Ncan't go higher than twenty, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She won't pay more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.75,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.88,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You just admitted that you're with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time... Please, Felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:31.01,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Begging won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:34.28,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I acknowledge you as a negotiating party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:37.02,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,But not hearing what my client \Nsays wouldn't be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:42.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I want that insignia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is so I can return it to its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.34,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to return it to its owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:50.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want the insignia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all! So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:22:00.36,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Felt, it doesn't look to me like the boy's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.42,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get taken in by him.
